name: MagicGenieWishlist
overview:
MagicGenieWishlist.com is a FREE gift registry / wishlist site which allows you to add any item from any store. Create and share customized wishlists with your family and friends to save ready for any gift giving occasion!

Creating wishlists for every memeber of your household on one account only takes a minute, then you add items at your leisure. Being able to save your family and friends wishlists makes it easy to find out what they would like the next time a gift giving occasion comes along.

Create wishlists for general use, or even create registries for weddings, baby showers etc. You can even create shopping lists of items you wish to purchase for yourself, then cross them off as you buy them. This can be used for moving house, the arrival of a new baby or anything else you may need this for.

Asking for money for weddings can be hard, so you can even choose large ticket items for your loved ones to make a contribution towards.

MagicGenieWishlist is fast, easy and a free service so you never run the risk of recieving another boring or duplicate gift again.
